---
import ContentLayout from "../layouts/ContentLayout.astro";
---

<ContentLayout
    title="Celebration of Education"
    description="Join us for our annual Celebration of Education event, recognizing outstanding students, educators, and community supporters."
    showBreadcrumbs={true}
    breadcrumbs={[
        { name: "Celebration of Education", href: "/celebration-of-education" }
    ]}
>
    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Annual Celebration of Education</h2>
        <p>
            The Green Schools Foundation's Annual Celebration of Education is our signature event, bringing together the entire community to recognize and celebrate academic excellence, outstanding educators, and the generous supporters who make our programs possible.
        </p>
        <p>
            This special evening showcases the achievements of our students, honors dedicated teachers and staff, and presents scholarships to graduating seniors. It's a time to reflect on our successes and look forward to the future of education in Green Local Schools.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="highlight-box">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-4">2025 Celebration of Education</h2>
        <div class="grid-2">
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Event Details</h3>
                <div class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6 2a1 1 0 00-1 1v1H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2h-1V3a1 1 0 10-2 0v1H7V3a1 1 0 00-1-1zm0 5a1 1 0 000 2h8a1 1 0 100-2H6z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span><strong>Date:</strong> Spring 2025 (TBA)</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-12a1 1 0 10-2 0v4a1 1 0 00.293.707l2.828 2.829a1 1 0 101.415-1.415L11 9.586V6z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span><strong>Time:</strong> 6:00 PM - 9:00 PM</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.05 4.05a7 7 0 119.9 9.9L10 18.9l-4.95-4.95a7 7 0 010-9.9zM10 11a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span><strong>Location:</strong> Green High School Auditorium</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Registration</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                    Registration details for the 2025 event will be announced soon. Check back for updates or subscribe to our newsletter to be notified.
                </p>
                <a href="mailto:greenschoolsfoundation@gmail.com?subject=Celebration of Education 2025" class="button-primary">
                    Get Updates
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>What to Expect</h2>
        <div class="grid-2">
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="flex items-start">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Student Recognition</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Celebrate the achievements of our Academy of Scholars, Laws of Life essay winners, and other outstanding students.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-start">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-accent-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path d="M10.394 2.08a1 1 0 00-.788 0l-7 3a1 1 0 000 1.84L5.25 8.051a.999.999 0 01.356-.257l4-1.714a1 1 0 11.788 1.838L7.667 9.088l1.94.831a1 1 0 00.787 0l7-3a1 1 0 000-1.838l-7-3zM3.31 9.397L5 10.12v4.102a8.969 8.969 0 00-1.05-.174 1 1 0 01-.89-.89 11.115 11.115 0 01.25-3.762zM9.3 16.573A9.026 9.026 0 007 14.935v-3.957l1.818.78a3 3 0 002.364 0l5.508-2.361a11.026 11.026 0 01.25 3.762 1 1 0 01-.89.89 8.968 8.968 0 00-5.35 2.524 1 1 0 01-1.4 0zM6 18a1 1 0 001-1v-2.065a8.935 8.935 0 00-2-.712V17a1 1 0 001 1z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Scholarship Awards</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Present scholarships to graduating seniors who will continue their educational journey.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-start">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-secondary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-secondary-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 9a3 3 0 100-6 3 3 0 000 6zm-7 9a7 7 0 1114 0H3z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Staff Spotlight</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Honor exceptional teachers and staff members who make a difference in our students' lives.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="flex items-start">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path d="M13 6a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zM18 8a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM14 15a4 4 0 00-8 0v3h8v-3z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Community Appreciation</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Recognize the generous donors, volunteers, and community partners who support our mission.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-start">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 3a1 1 0 00-1.447-.894L8.763 6H5a3 3 0 000 6h.28l1.771 5.316A1 1 0 008 18h1a1 1 0 001-1v-4.382l6.553 3.276A1 1 0 0018 15V3z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Inspiring Presentations</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Hear from student speakers, view project showcases, and learn about the impact of our programs.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-start">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3.172 5.172a4 4 0 015.656 0L10 6.343l1.172-1.171a4 4 0 115.656 5.656L10 17.657l-6.828-6.829a4 4 0 010-5.656z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Networking & Fellowship</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Connect with fellow community members who share a passion for educational excellence.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Past Celebrations</h2>
        <p class="mb-8">
            Each year, our Celebration of Education brings together hundreds of community members to honor achievements and support our students. Here are some highlights from recent years.
        </p>

        <div class="grid-2">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-600 mb-3">2024 Highlights</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 text-sm">
                    <li>• 25 scholarship recipients recognized</li>
                    <li>• $45,000 in scholarships awarded</li>
                    <li>• 15 Academy of Scholars honored</li>
                    <li>• 8 teachers received Staff Spotlight recognition</li>
                    <li>• Over 300 community members in attendance</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-accent-600 mb-3">2023 Highlights</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 text-sm">
                    <li>• 22 scholarship recipients recognized</li>
                    <li>• $42,000 in scholarships awarded</li>
                    <li>• 12 Academy of Scholars honored</li>
                    <li>• 6 teachers received Staff Spotlight recognition</li>
                    <li>• Laws of Life essay winners celebrated</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Event Sponsors & Partners</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
            Our Celebration of Education is made possible through the generous support of local businesses, community organizations, and individual donors. We gratefully acknowledge their contributions to making this event special.
        </p>

        <div class="text-center">
            <div class="inline-block bg-primary-50 px-8 py-6 rounded-lg">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-primary-800 mb-2">Interested in Sponsoring?</h3>
                <p class="text-primary-700 text-sm mb-4">
                    Support our celebration and gain recognition in the community
                </p>
                <a href="mailto:greenschoolsfoundation@gmail.com?subject=Event Sponsorship" class="button-primary">
                    Become a Sponsor
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="highlight-box">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-4">Join Us in Celebrating Excellence</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
            The Celebration of Education is more than an event—it's a testament to our community's commitment to academic excellence and student success. Whether you're a parent, educator, business owner, or community member, you're invited to be part of this special evening.
        </p>
        <div class="grid-2">
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">For Attendees</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 text-sm mb-4">
                    <li>• Witness inspiring student achievements</li>
                    <li>• Meet scholarship recipients and their families</li>
                    <li>• Learn about the impact of your support</li>
                    <li>• Connect with fellow community members</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="mailto:greenschoolsfoundation@gmail.com?subject=Celebration of Education Attendance" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 font-semibold">
                    Register to Attend →
                </a>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">For Volunteers</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 text-sm mb-4">
                    <li>• Help with event setup and coordination</li>
                    <li>• Assist with registration and greeting</li>
                    <li>• Support audio/visual needs</li>
                    <li>• Help with cleanup and breakdown</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="mailto:greenschoolsfoundation@gmail.com?subject=Volunteer Opportunity" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 font-semibold">
                    Volunteer With Us →
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section text-center">
        <h2>Stay Updated</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
            Be the first to know about our 2025 Celebration of Education event details, registration, and special announcements.
        </p>
        <a href="/blog" class="button-primary mr-4">Read Our Blog</a>
        <a href="mailto:greenschoolsfoundation@gmail.com?subject=Newsletter Subscription" class="button-secondary">Subscribe to Newsletter</a>
    </div>
</ContentLayout>
